Hot, hot, hot.

25:17.040 --> 25:19.542
Hot. Hot.

25:20.440 --> 25:22.199
Hot, hot.

25:22.200 --> 25:25.021
Hot. Hot.

25:25.440 --> 25:28.159
Hot. Uh-huh.

25:28.160 --> 25:31.664
♪♪ [WHISTLING]

25:37.680 --> 25:39.759
- That's pretty bad.
- What?

25:39.760 --> 25:42.239
I am totally keeping pace with you.

25:42.240 --> 25:45.279
[LAUGHS] Yeah, well,
it's a marathon. It's not a sprint.

25:45.280 --> 25:47.239
That sounds like loser talk...

25:47.240 --> 25:50.107
from someone who can't
keep up with a girl.

25:51.760 --> 25:53.759
Are you cheered up now?

25:53.760 --> 25:57.423
Yeah. Yeah, I'm cool. I just...
I worry about her. She's my sister.

25:57.800 --> 26:01.199
