that you care so much.

26:01.200 --> 26:03.065
Kayla, come on.

26:03.920 --> 26:06.159
Don't. It's fine. I'm...

26:06.160 --> 26:09.279
I'm gonna go find Amy before
I make a bigger fool of myself.

26:09.280 --> 26:12.519
Come on. You don't
even know this place.

26:12.520 --> 26:14.784
You're just gonna get lost.

26:16.920 --> 26:19.661
