- What?

26:19.920 --> 26:21.879
Why don't you like me?

26:21.880 --> 26:23.950
I like you.

26:25.120 --> 26:27.119
But...

26:27.120 --> 26:29.463
You're like a sister to me.

26:32.360 --> 26:36.865
♪♪ [SPEAKERS: ROCK]

26:45.080 --> 26:46.559
