- Yeah! Yeah! Yes! Yeah!
- Come on. Come on!

26:58.720 --> 27:00.999
Oh! Yes! Oh! Yes!

27:01.000 --> 27:03.839
- [GRUNTING, MOANING]
- Yes!

27:03.840 --> 27:06.820
[GRUNTING, MOANING CONTINUE]

27:10.040 --> 27:12.519
Yes! Oh! Oh!

27:12.520 --> 27:14.359
That's it! That's it!

27:14.360 --> 27:15.719
- Come on!
- Yes! Yes!

27:15.720 --> 27:17.519
- Right!
- Yeah!

27:17.520 --> 27:19.909
This is it! Oh!

27:20.960 --> 27:23.599
- Jacob?
- I'll be anyone you want me to be!

27:23.600 --> 27:24.639
Jacob?

27:24.640 --> 27:27.359
- No, no, no, look.
- [LAUGHS]

27:27.360 --> 27:30.159
- [EXHALES]
- Where's the body?

27:30.160 --> 27:32.439
- What?
- Shut up!

27:32.440 --> 27:35.181
It's just the guys messing around.

27:37.040 --> 27:39.239
No, no, no. No, no, wait. Hang on.

27:39.240 --> 27:41.959
How could they move the body?
How could they move the body?

27:41.960 --> 27:43.519
- I don't know.
- [TAMARA SCREAMS]

27:43.520 --> 27:46.227
- CARTER: Shit!
- TAMARA: Shit.

27:53.720 --> 27:54.959
Okay.

27:54.960 --> 27:57.399
Listen, take my hand.

27:57.400 --> 27:59.879
Don't let go. Okay?

27:59.880 --> 28:01.639
There's the door.
I see light coming through.

28:01.640 --> 28:04.222
- Someone's just being a dick.
- Okay.

28:04.520 --> 28:06.679
If someone's just being a dick...

28:06.680 --> 28:08.519
why are you whispering?

28:08.520 --> 28:09.879
- What?
- What?

28:09.880 --> 28:11.506
Ow! Shit!

28:23.400 --> 28:25.239
Guys?

28:25.240 --> 28:27.230
You down here?

28:28.880 --> 28:31.199
- Okay, let's go.
- Okay.

28:31.200 --> 28:33.270
Oh! Ow! Ow! Ow!

28:35.280 --> 28:37.439
CARTER: Shh. Shh.

28:37.440 --> 28:39.590
Did you hear that?

28:49.280 --> 28:51.703
[SCREAMING]

28:53.480 --> 28:56.267
[TAMARA SCREAMING]

29:04.440 --> 29:07.944
[SCREAMING CONTINUES]

29:51.000 --> 29:54.709
Once your soul's clean,
you'll be the hand of God.

29:55.160 --> 29:57.839
I see that! I see what you're doing.

29:57.840 --> 30:00.239
[WHIMPERING, SOBBING]

30:00.240 --> 30:04.599
What are you doing? Let go!
Ungrateful bastard! You hear me?

30:04.600 --> 30:06.704
Don't you see the sin?

30:07.440 --> 30:09.239
[SOBBING]

30:09.240 --> 30:11.919
I s... I see it.

30:11.920 --> 30:14.991
[JACOB CONTINUES SOBBING]

30:24.120 --> 30:26.941
- [CARTER GROANING]
- [JACOB SOBBING]

30:38.320 --> 30:40.424
[WHIMPERING] Oh, man, I'm sorry.

30:40.800 --> 30:43.719
I see...

30:43.720 --> 30:45.824
it!

30:46.040 --> 30:47.780
Please! Please!

30:48.680 --> 30:50.399
No, man! I'm sorry!

30:50.400 --> 30:53.719
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
I m sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

30:53.720 --> 30:55.919
All right? Please! Please! Let me go!

30:55.920 --> 30:58.039
- Please let me go!
- I see it!

30:58.040 --> 31:00.719
- [GROANING]
- [JACOB ROARING]

31:00.720 --> 31:02.399
[CRUNCHING]

31:02.400 --> 31:05.744
[GASPING, CHOKING]

31:15.120 --> 31:18.146
[TAMARA SCREAMING]

31:34.680 --> 31:37.228
[SCREAMING]

32:13.880 --> 32:17.279
[WAILING] Oh! No! Oh!

32:17.280 --> 32:19.479
You guys! No!

32:19.480 --> 32:21.399
Oh, God! This is bad! This is so bad!

32:21.400 --> 32:22.639
This is so bad!

32:22.640 --> 32:25.879
You guys! You guys!

32:25.880 --> 32:29.111
[TAMARA CONTINUES SCREAMING]

32:31.640 --> 32:33.790
What the hell?

32:53.600 --> 32:55.959
[TAMARA SCREAMS, DISTANT]

32:55.960 --> 32:58.599
- Hold on.
- [SIGHS] What?

32:58.600 --> 33:00.959
- I heard a scream.
- Oh, did you?

33:00.960 --> 33:02.507
Oh.

33:02.720 --> 33:05.279
I didn't hear anything.

33:05.280 --> 33:08.919
- [SCREAMING CONTINUES]
- Oh, God. Tamara.

33:08.920 --> 33:11.239
She's just messing around, right?

33:11.240 --> 33:13.344
We should check it out.

33:15.200 --> 33:16.919
Seriously?

33:16.920 --> 33:18.999
- What?
- I don't know.

33:19.000 --> 33:22.079
I panicked, and then
I just attacked him.

33:22.080 --> 33:25.359
Oh, my God, Kayla. Really tactful.

33:25.360 --> 33:26.839
I know.

33:26.840 --> 33:29.581
But it still counts as
progress though, right?

33:33.840 --> 33:36.342
Any of you jokers down here?

33:36.760 --> 33:40.230
Look, I'm not gonna
do this all night!

33:52.320 --> 33:55.744
Help! Help!

33:56.440 --> 33:58.101
Help!

34:01.360 --> 34:04.261
[YELLS, WHIMPERING]

34:10.719 --> 34:12.824
[CHAIN RATTLES]

34:24.600 --> 34:26.625
[GROANING]

34:37.440 --> 34:41.467
[SCREAMING] No! No!

34:42.800 --> 34:44.824
[HOLDEN SCREAMS, MUFFLED]

34:46.560 --> 34:48.839
- That doesn't sound like messing around.
- That came from downstairs.

34:48.840 --> 34:51.103
Come on. This way.

34:52.840 --> 34:54.909
[BELL DINGS]

35:11.080 --> 35:13.150
Where did the body go?

35:13.840 --> 35:15.519
- What body?
- The...

35:15.520 --> 35:17.519
- Jacob Goodnight.
- Jacob who?

35:17.520 --> 35:20.159
The guy who killed everyone
at the Blackwell Hotel.

35:20.160 --> 35:22.389
Hey.

35:23.720 --> 35:25.551
Gross!

35:29.200 --> 35:31.159
Oh, my God!

35:31.160 --> 35:34.186
[SCREAMING]

35:37.480 --> 35:39.982
What the heck?

35:41.400 --> 35:44.359
- [SWITCH CLICKING]
- [SIGHS]

35:44.360 --> 35:47.466
[CLICK]

35:48.120 --> 35:50.702
That sucks less.

36:01.720 --> 36:05.239
My God! Who did that to Carter?

36:05.240 --> 36:06.839
[GASPING] Where's Tamara?

36:06.840 --> 36:10.279
- Oh, my... Oh, my God!
- When was the last time you saw her?

36:10.280 --> 36:12.319
I don't know! She left with Carter!

36:12.320 --> 36:14.879
Okay, the first thing we
need to do is call the cops.

36:14.880 --> 36:17.719
But our phones are
locked in the office!

36:17.720 --> 36:20.239
- Oh, God!
- Okay! Calm down!

36:20.240 --> 36:22.199
[STAMMERING]

36:22.200 --> 36:24.919
Give me your... Give me your lighter.

36:24.920 --> 36:26.439
- Here you go.
- Thank you. Okay.

36:26.440 --> 36:28.783
- Okay.
- Okay.

36:30.400 --> 36:32.159
Okay. We have to find them.

36:32.160 --> 36:33.639
Come on. Let's go.

36:33.640 --> 36:36.188
[KAYLA SOBBING]

36:38.600 --> 36:42.263
- [SOBBING CONTINUES]
- Okay, guys, quiet.

36:46.600 --> 36:48.704
Give me a break.

36:50.160 --> 36:52.264
[KEYS JINGLING]

36:55.760 --> 36:58.740
♪♪ [WHISTLING]

37:01.160 --> 37:03.264
Hey, guys?

37:05.200 --> 37:07.399
Amy?

37:07.400 --> 37:09.425
Holden?

37:10.280 --> 37:12.623
Amy's friends?

37:30.080 --> 37:33.584
[CLANKING]

37:47.160 --> 37:49.839
KAYLA:
It's not working! What do we do now?

37:49.840 --> 37:52.439
Okay, we're here. We need
to take the stairwell here.

37:52.440 --> 37:56.519
Is that the only way out? What if
whoever did that to Carter is up there?

37:56.520 --> 37:58.179
The stairs are the only way.
We head up now,

37:58.180 --> 37:59.679
we can be out of here
in 10 minutes flat.

37:59.680 --> 38:02.359
- No!
- Amy, no, wait! Amy! Wait!

38:02.360 --> 38:04.679
[KAYLA GASPS] What is that?

38:04.680 --> 38:07.228
[GASPING CONTINUES]

38:08.280 --> 38:11.351
- Shh.
- [KAYLA CONTINUES GASPING]

38:17.880 --> 38:19.984
Shh!

38:30.840 --> 38:33.439
- Amy, don't go over there.
- Shh!

38:33.440 --> 38:35.199
[WHISPERING] No.

38:35.200 --> 38:37.304
Oh, my God!

38:43.120 --> 38:46.908
- Okay. Okay.
- [HOLDEN GASPS]

38:47.640 --> 38:50.188
- Oh, God.
- [HOLDEN COUGHS]

38:51.440 --> 38:54.359
[WHIMPERING] Oh, my God. Oh, my God.

38:54.360 --> 38:57.784
- I don't know what to do.
- [GASPING, COUGHING]

39:07.480 --> 39:09.869
[KAYLA WHISPERS] Amy.

39:10.240 --> 39:12.230
Oh, God.

39:13.000 --> 39:17.186
[WHIMPERING]
I'm sorry. I don't know what to do.

39:18.080 --> 39:20.119
WILL: Let's go.

39:20.120 --> 39:23.191
[SOBBING]

39:25.480 --> 39:28.381
- Let's go.
- Let's go this way.

39:48.000 --> 39:50.150
Christ!

39:51.520 --> 39:54.022
- [SIGHS]
- [CLANKING]

39:58.200 --> 40:00.270
Who's there?

40:07.680 --> 40:11.070
[CLANKING]

40:21.960 --> 40:24.462
[CLANKING]

40:46.320 --> 40:49.159
- [SCREAMING]
- Oh, my God.

40:49.160 --> 40:52.519
Hey! Oh, my God! Come here.
Come here. It's okay.

40:52.520 --> 40:54.359
[SCREAMING]

40:54.360 --> 40:56.159
Are you bleeding? You're bleeding!

40:56.160 --> 40:59.199
It's not my blood. It's Carter's!

40:59.200 --> 41:01.199
You're gonna be okay.
We're gonna stick together.

41:01.200 --> 41:04.439
No! He's dead! He killed him!

41:04.440 --> 41:06.719
- Who?
- Jacob. Jacob. Jacob Goodnight!

41:06.720 --> 41:08.959
No. No way.

41:08.960 --> 41:11.679
- Jacob Goodnight is dead.
- No! It was him!

41:11.680 --> 41:14.706
- He's a goddamn corpse!
- It was him!

41:15.200 --> 41:17.599
Jacob Goodnight is not dead.

41:17.600 --> 41:20.519
He's not dead. He's not dead anymore.

41:20.520 --> 41:24.759
He probably faked it so he
wouldn't have to get locked up.

41:24.760 --> 41:27.759
I don't know. He's in here now,
and we really pissed him off.

41:27.760 --> 41:30.706
Whoa, whoa. What do you
mean, "We pissed him off?"

41:30.720 --> 41:32.639
I thought he was dead.

41:32.640 --> 41:34.426
Tamara, what did you do?

41:36.800 --> 41:40.119
He got up while Carter
and I were, you know...

41:40.120 --> 41:42.799
KAYLA: Oh, my God! Are you kidding me?
You did it in the morgue?

41:42.800 --> 41:45.359
I thought he was dead!

41:45.360 --> 41:48.022
Shh!

41:49.920 --> 41:54.220
Uh, have you s... have you seen Seth?

41:57.440 --> 41:58.679
No. No. No.

41:58.680 --> 42:01.421
We have to go find him.

42:01.480 --> 42:04.039
Oh! Oh! Where's... wheelchair guy?

42:04.040 --> 42:06.959
Holden... Uh, Holden's dead.

42:06.960 --> 42:09.159
[WHIMPERING]

42:09.160 --> 42:12.439
Oh, God. Oh, God. Please tell me
you know how to get out of here.

42:12.440 --> 42:15.750
Yeah. It's just a little
bit further. Come on.

42:57.720 --> 43:00.268
Oh, man.

43:02.440 --> 43:04.624
[CLANKING]

43:06.240 --> 43:08.105
What the hell?

43:08.800 --> 43:10.839
What the hell?

43:10.840 --> 43:14.184
[SETH SCREAMING, WHIMPERING]

43:28.120 --> 43:29.985
Come on. This way.

43:31.320 --> 43:34.790
[TAMARA BABBLING]

43:38.120 --> 43:40.159
Stupid door! [GRUNTS]

43:40.160 --> 43:42.239
- Now what are we gonna do?
- [CHATTERING, SHRIEKING]

43:42.240 --> 43:45.399
It's a security door, Will.
That's not gonna work.

43:45.400 --> 43:47.239
Is there another way out?

43:47.240 --> 43:50.079
- Oh, my God! We're trapped!
- I don't want to do this.

43:50.080 --> 43:52.344
Hold on. Let me think!

43:53.000 --> 43:55.599
- [THUDDING]
- Amy!

43:55.600 --> 43:58.023
- Open the door!
- KAYLA: Open it!

43:58.440 --> 44:01.102
WILL: Open the door, Seth!

44:03.960 --> 44:05.839
Come on, come on, come on!

44:05.840 --> 44:08.599
- You okay?
- [SHRIEKING, CHATTERING]

44:08.600 --> 44:11.679
- Why are you locking the door?
- Jacob Goodnight is alive!

44:11.680 --> 44:13.599
He killed Holden and Carter.

44:13.600 --> 44:15.989
[SCREAMING]

44:16.480 --> 44:18.823
- No!
- [GRUNTING]

44:20.520 --> 44:22.679
[WHIMPERING]

44:22.680 --> 44:25.706
- Let's go!
- Go, go, go! Amy!

44:27.120 --> 44:28.759
Come on! Let's go!

44:28.760 --> 44:32.230
[SCREAMING CONTINUES]

44:42.400 --> 44:44.390
This way.

44:49.320 --> 44:51.039
- [WHISPERING] Here.
- Okay.

44:51.040 --> 44:53.959
- Let's go!
- Go!

44:53.960 --> 44:55.461
Come on!

44:55.960 --> 44:57.586
Slow down!

45:02.240 --> 45:05.999
[GASPING, WHIMPERING]

45:06.000 --> 45:07.501
Guys?

45:09.080 --> 45:11.150
Amy?

45:11.920 --> 45:13.910
Will?

45:15.760 --> 45:19.070
[SOBBING] Somebody? Please.

45:21.600 --> 45:24.199
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

45:24.200 --> 45:27.226
Oh, my God! Oh, my God. Oh, my...

45:29.920 --> 45:32.024
Shit.

45:33.840 --> 45:36.439
- You know where you're going, right?
- Yeah.

45:36.440 --> 45:38.079
Usually.

45:38.080 --> 45:41.159
Look, just stay close. Nothing
ever good comes of splitting up.

45:41.160 --> 45:44.119
- Let's go. In here.
- Will, slow down.

45:44.120 --> 45:46.782
- Amy, get in here!
- What? Why?

45:48.080 --> 45:49.439
No! No! No!

45:49.440 --> 45:51.639
Great, Will! Now we lost everybody.

45:51.640 --> 45:53.999
It's not my fault your
friends can't keep up!

45:54.000 --> 45:56.079
- He's out there!
- So are my friends!

45:56.080 --> 45:58.839
And if they have any sense,
they'll hide, like us.

45:58.840 --> 46:00.239
You are so selfish.

46:00.240 --> 46:02.559
I've seen you pull some
pretty low crap...

46:02.560 --> 46:04.999
but I don't even know
who you are right now.

46:05.000 --> 46:06.575
Because I don't want
to just charge out...

46:06.576 --> 46:10.824
when there's some mass murderer
hanging out? Think about it.

46:11.440 --> 46:13.669
I'm not letting him kill you.

46:15.240 --> 46:18.869
[WHIMPERING, SOBBING]

46:32.160 --> 46:34.662
- Please.
- [FOOTSTEPS]

46:37.560 --> 46:40.347
- [CLANKING]
- [WHIMPERING, SOBBING CONTINUE]

46:40.840 --> 46:44.399
Someone help me. Help me.

46:44.400 --> 46:46.982
- [DOOR OPENS]
- [GASPING]

46:49.000 --> 46:51.309
Oh, my gosh.

46:58.200 --> 47:00.702
[DOOR HANDLE RATTLES]

47:02.640 --> 47:05.142
